okay, so, now, I'd like to switch over to building up each district, one at a time. In each district, what sorts of things would you find there, what sorts of characters would live there, what would people's lives be like (whether they're robot or human), what sorts of daily routines would common, regular people have, etc etc. I'd like to really go into detail.}
