\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af9\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\widctlpar\hyphpar0\aspalpha\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af10\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa283\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Scorpio District \u8211\'96 The ThresholdOverview / Atmosphere\line The Threshold is Concordia\u8217\'92s psychological underworld \u8212\'97 the district where people (and robots) come when they need to break, burn, confront hidden truths, or remake themselves entirely. It is intense, secretive, transformative, and magnetically heavy. The atmosphere is deliberately dim and intimate. Deep crimson, violet, and dark amber lighting dominates. Steam rises from geothermal vents that run through the district. Architecture feels half-melted or deliberately scarred, as if the buildings themselves have survived trauma and been reborn. Sound is muted but resonant \u8212\'97 distant choral chanting, low-frequency hums, and the occasional sharp echo of something breaking or being rebuilt.This district does not offer easy comfort. It offers confrontation and rebirth. Many residents describe it as the place where you go when you can no longer pretend.Physical Environment & Landmarks}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls29 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
The Rebirth Clinics \u8212\'97 Private facilities offering extreme therapy, voluntary memory editing, body modification, and \u8220\'93death-rehearsal\u8221\'94 programs.}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls29 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
The Archive of Final Confessions \u8212\'97 A vast, quiet repository where people record final messages, traumas, or truths they need to leave behind.}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls29 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Endurance Arenas \u8212\'97 Ritualistic (consensual) spaces for physical and psychological endurance tests, duels, and transformation ceremonies.}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls29 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Deep Geothermal Meditation Chambers \u8212\'97 Cavernous rooms built around natural geothermal vents for intense introspection and sensory deprivation work.}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls29 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Shadow Augmentation Parlors \u8212\'97 Legal and semi-legal clinics for radical body and mind modifications.}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls29 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
The Veil Theater \u8212\'97 A performance space that specializes in dark, psychologically intense art exploring grief, loss, desire, and rebirth.}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls29 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
