\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af9\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\widctlpar\hyphpar0\aspalpha\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af10\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa283\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Aquarius District \u8211\'96 Ascendant Research QuarterOverview / Atmosphere\line The Ascendant Research Quarter is Concordia\u8217\'92s forward-looking, eccentric, and visionary brain \u8212\'97 the district dedicated to experimentation, breakthroughs, and pushing the boundaries of what is possible. It has a clean, futuristic, slightly chaotic feel. The air is crisp and cool (heavily filtered and climate-controlled), with a faint ozone and metallic scent from active experiments. Lighting is bright white and cool blue, often mixed with shifting holographic displays and prototype glows.This district feels like the future trying to be born in the middle of a dying city. It is optimistic, intellectually intense, and sometimes dangerously detached from the immediate suffering in other districts. The architecture is sleek, modular, and experimental \u8212\'97 lots of glass, white composites, and open layouts that allow for rapid reconfiguration of labs.Physical Environment & Landmarks}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls53 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
The Ascendant Tower \u8212\'97 The central spire that houses the most advanced labs and administrative offices. It glows softly at night with experimental lighting.}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls53 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
