\par \pard\plain \s0\rtlch\af9\afs24\alang1081 \ltrch\lang1033\langfe2052\hich\af3\loch\widctlpar\hyphpar0\aspalpha\ltrpar\cf0\f3\fs24\lang1033\kerning1\dbch\af10\langfe2052\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa283\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Libra District \u8211\'96 Governmental ApexOverview / Atmosphere\line The Governmental Apex is the political and administrative center of Concordia \u8212\'97 the district responsible for law, resource allocation, diplomacy, and maintaining (or attempting to maintain) balance across the entire city. It has a formal, elegant, and somewhat austere atmosphere. Architecture is grand but restrained: tall polished metal and glass structures, symmetrical layouts, and wide open plazas designed for public gatherings and debates.The air is crisp and well-filtered. Lighting is clean and neutral, with soft white and cool blue tones. There is a constant low hum of activity \u8212\'97 holographic displays, quiet debates, the rustle of documents, and the occasional echo of public announcements. It feels important, bureaucratic, and strained under the weight of impossible decisions during the energy crisis.This is the district where the ideals of fairness, justice, and unity are constantly tested against harsh reality.Physical Environment & Landmarks}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls61 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
The Grand Council Chambers \u8212\'97 The central legislative hall where major city-wide decisions are debated and voted on. It has a large circular layout with seating for representatives from every district.}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls61 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Treaty Archive Vaults \u8212\'97 Secure, climate-controlled archives holding records of the Falkland Treaty, pre-war agreements, and post-war accords.}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls61 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Bureau of Resource Allocation \u8212\'97 The most stressed and heavily guarded building in the district. This is where power, heat, siligel, and materials are distributed (and fought over).}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls61 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Diplomatic Reception Halls \u8212\'97 Elegant spaces used for negotiations between districts and factions.}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls61 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Justice & Arbitration Courts \u8212\'97 Formal courtrooms where disputes between districts, factions, or individuals are resolved.}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls61 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Public Policy Announcement Plazas \u8212\'97 Open areas where major announcements are made and citizens can voice concerns (though during the crisis these gatherings are often tense).}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls61 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
The Scales Atrium \u8212\'97 A grand central hall with a massive symbolic sculpture representing balance and justice. It serves as a meeting point and symbolic heart of the district.}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140\fi0\li0\lin0\ri0\rin0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Inhabitants (Humans & Robots)}
