Gemini District \u8211\'96 Janbogo Subnet NexusOverview / Atmosphere\line The Janbogo Subnet Nexus is Concordia\u8217\'92s nervous system \u8212\'97 the district of information, communication, data flow, and connectivity. It is bright, fast-paced, ever-changing, and humming with activity. The air is crisp and cool from heavy climate control. You are surrounded by the constant glow of holographic displays, scrolling data streams, and the low chatter of thousands of simultaneous conversations. Architecture is open and layered, with transparent floors, elevated walkways, and walls covered in live Arcanet feeds. Everything feels interconnected and in motion.This district is curious, talkative, and sometimes chaotic. It is where rumors are born, news spreads at lightspeed, and the city\u8217\'92s collective consciousness is both maintained and manipulated.Physical Environment & Landmarks}
