Pisces District \u8211\'96 The Veil MarketOverview / Atmosphere\line The Veil Market is Concordia\u8217\'92s shadow economy and black-market heart \u8212\'97 a district of deals, desperation, opportunity, and moral gray areas. It is lively, dimly lit, and constantly shifting. The air carries a mix of incense, street food, ozone from illegal tech, and the faint metallic tang of smuggled siligel. Lighting is low and atmospheric \u8212\'97 deep purples, warm ambers, and flickering neon signs that advertise everything from \u8220\'93legitimate\u8221\'94 goods to clearly illegal services.This district feels alive in a sly, watchful way. Everyone is here for something they can\u8217\'92t (or won\u8217\'92t) get through official channels. It is equal parts helpful and exploitative, generous and cutthroat. The Veil Market doesn\u8217\'92t pretend to be moral \u8212\'97 it simply exists to fill the gaps left by the failing official system.Physical Environment & Landmarks}
