Sagittarius District \u8211\'96 Frostward ReachesOverview / Atmosphere\line The Frostward Reaches is Concordia\u8217\'92s wild frontier \u8212\'97 the outermost district where the city meets the raw, unforgiving Antarctic ice. It is bold, independent, rugged, and fiercely self-reliant. The air is bitterly cold and crisp, with a constant bite of wind even inside the domes. You smell frozen metal, machine oil, preserved food, and the faint ozone of struggling heaters. Architecture is practical and fortified: reinforced domes, heavy blast doors, and modular structures designed to withstand extreme weather. Lighting is functional and harsh \u8212\'97 bright whites and cold blues during work hours, shifting to warm emergency reds during storms or blackouts. The district has a frontier spirit: optimistic yet pragmatic, adventurous yet survival-focused. People here see themselves as the ones who push the boundaries while the inner districts grow soft.Physical Environment & Landmarks}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls85 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
The Outer Ring Domes \u8212\'97 Heavily reinforced habitation and work domes built to withstand blizzards and ice quakes.}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls85 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Kharkovchanka Depots & Vehicle Bays \u8212\'97 Massive garages housing the district\u8217\'92s fleet of rugged, cold-resistant transport vehicles.}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls85 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
Ice Harvesting & Resource Outposts \u8212\'97 Facilities where crews extract rare minerals, water ice, and exotic compounds from the surrounding glaciers.}
\par \pard\plain \s17\loch\sl276\slmult1\sb0\sa140{\listtext\pard\plain \rtlch\af5 \ltrch\hich\af5\loch\f5\dbch\af5 \u57352\'3f\tab}\ilvl0\ls85 \fi-283\li0\lin0\tx709\fi-283\li709\lin709\ri0\rin0\sb0\sa0\ltrpar{\hich\af4\loch\cf1\f4\loch
